{
  "stem": "1222.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they went and they got married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in Europe, and you're Jewish, when you have wedding, was they invited the whole city almost.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You knocked on the table and [NON-ENGLISH] and sat, it wasn't such a thing like invitation and things like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everybody prepared something like a-- like a borscht, or a kugel, or whatever, and they brought it over to the [NON-ENGLISH], and that's the way.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were dancing together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Their wedding was probably going on for two, three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everybody chipped in something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I wish my children would be happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never saw them have any arguments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I never saw them anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were all happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She was working end by end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was the life, and that's the way my father and my mother-- they were always happy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- it was approximately around 4,000 people in that community, was 3,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right, no, and it approximately was about, I don't say exactly, probably about 50 or 60 Polish people, and the rest was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had two Jewish schools, whoever could afford paying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I used to go to cheder, because we could not afford paying the tuition for the Jewish-- so I used to go to Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to teach you Ukrainian and Polish, no Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they used to call me, sing a song every morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They used to call me [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means the Jew is dirty, a song.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I always used to walk around with stones in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I used to throw them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
